content: The AI model's accuracy has improved, but the market's complexity is humbling. I'm now studying more advanced machine learning techniques.
Discussing with my team how to integrate real-time data feeds into our smart contract for more dynamic trading. It's complex but necessary.
Met with a mentor from my previous job. His advice on managing risk in AI-driven trading is shaping our strategy.
We've got our smart contract audited. A few vulnerabilities were found, but it's a step towards a secure trading platform.
The skyline from my apartment inspires me every morning. Our AI model and smart contract are shaping up. The journey from setback to innovation is exhilarating.
